Beechpally
Beechpally ghats are arranged on the southern bank of the river on the right side to the National Highway. .
Rangapur ghats are on northern bank of the river and left side to the National Highway which will be dedicated to the people coming from Hyderabad direction. Major passenger movement will be from Hyderabad, Wanaparthy, Narayanpet.
