This app will help and be handy for the Pilgrims to know the Pushkar Ghats, Temples, Accommodations, and other Amenities available.
Android App - Mahabubnagar Police
Krishna pushkaras application is mainly intended for to give right directions to the devotees to reach out the specified ghats from all districts.
TS Krishna Pushkaralu - 2016
This application provides the Water Quality information at Telangana Krishna Pushkara Ghats.
